---
layout: base
title: "Water Filtration Reviews"
description: "Engineering-grade reviews of home water filtration systems. Under-sink RO systems, countertop pitchers, gravity filters — honest specs, real TCO analysis."
permalink: /reviews/water/
---

<div class="container" style="padding-top: 2rem;">

  <h1>Water Filtration Reviews</h1>
  <p class="category-intro">Independent, specification-driven reviews for homeowners who treat water quality as infrastructure — not an afterthought.</p>

  <div class="review-list">
    {% for review in collections.waterReviews | reverse %}
    <article class="review-card">
      <h2><a href="{{ review.url }}">{{ review.data.title }}</a></h2>
      {% if review.data.description %}<p>{{ review.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
      {% if review.data.date %}<time>{{ review.data.date | dateFormat }}</time>{% endif %}
      <a href="{{ review.url }}" class="read-more">Read full review →</a>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

</div>
